creator: Fudy OÜ
descriptionHtml:
By being built exclusively around the food and the restaurant industry – we offer a more distilled, refined and relevant experience for foodies wherever they might be, whether at home or at work. The food experience will always be at the center of our focus.

We strive to create meaningful and memorable experiences. We understand that there is a symbiotic ecosystem between restauranteur, customers and foodies alike. We aim to continually engage and grow by investing and developing in systems that benefit the foodie community.
descriptionShort: Fudy is about — Food, Friends, Family

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Google Pay is now available. Pay swiftly without ever adding your card details to the app.

• Best of Fudy 2022 - Find the most loved restaurants on the "Best of Fudy" carousel. Category winners were selected based of the actual order data.

• Introducing Delivery promotions 🎁 - Get discounts on delivery when you're spending over displayed amount. Currently available on many selected restaurants that you can find by delivery promo badge.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Thanks to pins, it’s easier to track your order now.

• Sign up for our newsletters with one click in settings. Or unsubscribe. You decide.

• We painted some buttons so the app looks a bit more appealing to your eyes now.

• We have added extra steps for ordering alcohol.

• You can now rely on the restaurant opening times.

• Open the app to see what else is new.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• A new search feature – you can search a specific food from the restaurant’s menu. Super easy, if you know what you want to eat!

• Improved location sharing allows the courier to find you faster.

• Better order tracking improves visibility for the entire order’s journey so you know exactly where your food is.

• It is now easier to invite friends via a banner (and earn credits while doing it)!

• We also simplified the rating process so now you can rate the order right after delivery.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Make sure to update the app because we have quite many improvements for you! Some bigger ones:

– when searching inside the restaurant, you’ll first see the products that are matching with your keyword
– you’ll now get a note before paying if your current location differs from your delivery address
– couriers are now more likely to see your delivery notes
– no more unnecessary grey screens and broken texts!
